      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "IMP: Parenthesis are required for older versions of hibernate. Newer versions will not support () - at least in my case. Also, see this solution <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/a/21341663/6043669\">stackoverflow.com/a/21341663/6043669</a>"
