  "title" : "IN-clause in HQL or Java Persistence Query Language",
  "body" : "<p>My parametrised JPA or Hibernate query:</p>\n<pre><code>SELECT entity FROM Entity entity WHERE name IN (?)\n</code></pre>\n<p>How can I pass the parameter as an <code>ArrayList&lt;String&gt;</code>? Hibernate currently returns:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>java.lang.ClassCastException: java.util.ArrayList cannot be cast to java.lang.String</p>\n</blockquote>\n"
